	<ResearchProjectDef ParentName="GW_ImperiumTechBase">
		<defName>GW_DrugProduction</defName>
		<label>imperium drug production</label>
        <description>Allows for the production of various mind altering substances common throughout the imperium, from fenrisian ale to combat stims. Fenrisian Ale, called Mj√∏d in the unique Fenrisian Low Gothic dialect, is an extremely potent concoction distilled from the fermentation of the native plants of Fenris. Battle stimulants basicly works as massive power boost, but have cost of addiction.</description>
		<prerequisites>
			<li>GW_Cogitator</li>
			<li>DrugProduction</li>
		</prerequisites>
        <baseCost>2000</baseCost>
		<researchViewX>0.00</researchViewX>
		<researchViewY>0.00</researchViewY>
	</ResearchProjectDef>

	<ResearchProjectDef ParentName="GW_ImperiumTechBase">
		<defName>GW_PlasmaReactor</defName>
		<label>plasma reactor</label>
        <description>Allows for the creation of the plasma generator, a massive structure that converts uranium into electricity. Uses uranium to generate massive amount of power.</description>
